{
  "stem": "14251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it would be safest if I didn't know [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who I was, what we were, if I had no comprehension.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so in 1941, they stopped doing-- I remember my mother mentions a Seder dinner that my grandfather said, suddenly, when the main part was done, clear all this off.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Get rid of all this off the table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Get this out of here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't want to see it again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, you have to realize my grandmother had just passed away with the cancer business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Nazi thing had zeroed in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Forced labor was in effect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so, out you could not get.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where would you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we now learn, any of those who did go out-- say, to Holland or France-- that was all just temporary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They ran from country to country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not possible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And without money, which none of us had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That had already-- we had been relieved of anything that would represent money or value.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to know more what you mean by that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Best as I can tell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, it apparently turned out I was very outgoing, and my mother called me her chatter box, so that I was, at times, a danger to the circumstances that followed-- in the years that followed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She always had to stay within earshot to make sure, to call me away as I was about to play, say, telephone with a girl named Uta, a German girl, by the time we were underground.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- we each pretended we had a telephone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother heard Uta, hier Evy Go-- I wasn't supposed to say my name.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
